@startuml
[*] --> Idle
Idle --> WaitingForVoice: start_recording()

state WaitingForVoice {
  [*] --> Monitoring
  Monitoring: on_chunk: volume = get_volume()
  Monitoring --> VoiceDetected: volume > voice_threshold
}

VoiceDetected --> Recording: [true]
Recording: on_chunk: append_frame()
Recording --> CheckingForSilence: volume < silence_threshold
Recording --> Recording: volume >= silence_threshold

CheckingForSilence: on_chunk: silence_count++
CheckingForSilence --> Recording: volume > silence_threshold
CheckingForSilence --> Finalizing: silence_count >= silence_duration

Finalizing --> Done: encode_to_wav(frames)
Done --> [*]
@enduml